      "review_summary": "The branch adds a default-off repair feature flag, changes repair and issue-implementation concurrency to explicit one-run defaults, prefers portable gitcrawl-store databases, and updates related workflows, docs, and tests.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Source inspection is sufficient: current main always passes --execute for targeted synced-verdict routing, while the PR head omits it unless CLAWSWEEPER_FEATURE_REPAIR_ENABLED is exactly 1 and defaults that variable to 0.",
